	* doc/geomview.texi: {RG}b to {RGB}

	* doc/geomview.texi:
	"Draw" to "Show" and "right" to "left" in Appearence panel.
	Faces, Edges, Normals, BBox and Vects are under "show"
	and not under "draw" and in "upper left corner" and not in
	"upper right corner".

