	* src/lib/gprim/mesh/meshdraw.c, src/lib/gprim/ndmesh/ndmeshdraw.c, src/lib/gprim/npolylist/npldraw.c, src/lib/gprim/polylist/pldraw.c, src/lib/gprim/quad/quaddraw.c, src/lib/mg/opengl/mgopengldraw.c:
